description: Itty Bitty Donuts is Nashville's mini donut food truck.  They serve up hot, delicious, made-to-order mini donuts.  They offer a variety of specialty sugars, as well as their famous Donut Sundaes, which feature a wide assortment of appetizing toppings. Looking for a fun, different idea for your event?  Itty Bitty Donuts can provide you and your guests with a delicious alternative at your next gathering.
name: Itty Bitty Donuts
